  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
A <fr:link href="/gtop-000C/" title="Borel Measure" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000C/" display-uri="gtop-000C" type="local">Borel measure</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu ]]></fr:tex> on a <fr:link href="/gtop-0002/" title="Topological Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0002/" display-uri="gtop-0002" type="local">topological space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is <html:strong>inner regular</html:strong> on a <fr:link href="/gtop-000L/" title="Borel Set" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000L/" display-uri="gtop-000L" type="local">Borel set</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex> if
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
\mu (E) = \sup  \left \{  \mu (M) : M \subseteq  E, \; M \text { is compact}  \right \}
]]></fr:tex>
where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="/gtop-0008/" title="Compactness" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0008/" display-uri="gtop-0008" type="local">compact</fr:link> subset.
</html:p>
    <html:p>
That is, the measure of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex> can be approximated from below by the measures of <fr:link href="/gtop-0008/" title="Compactness" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0008/" display-uri="gtop-0008" type="local">compact</fr:link> subsets of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
